方法详细信息

reallocateRegister

public static int reallocateRegister(TargetCode targetCode,
                                     int k,
                                     int reserved)
Reallocate registers in targetCode with registers 0 ~ k-1. Registers 0 ~ reserved-1 are reserved for special use.

参数：
targetCode -
k -
reserved -
返回：
Maximum number of registers used after the re-allocation. If anything goes wrong, -1 is returned.
